        {
            "parameters": {
                "content": "## Workflow 2B \u2013 Job Response Handler\n\n**Webhook:** GET /webhook/job-response\n**Query params:** bookingUid, cleanerId, response (accept|decline)\n\nCalled when a cleaner clicks Accept or Decline in their offer email.\n\n- **Accept:** creates calendar events, generates clock-in/out links, sends confirmation email, sets status=ASSIGNED\n- **Decline:** adds cleaner to declinedBy, resets status=PENDING so Workflow 2 offers to next cleaner\n- **Error:** invalid params, job not OFFERED, or wrong cleaner",
                "height": 340,
                "width": 360
            },
            "id": "10b00002-aaaa-4bbb-cccc-dd0000000002",
            "name": "Sticky Note",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
            "typeVersion": 1,
            "position": [-200, -500]
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "jsCode": "const item = $input.first().json;\nconst query = item.query || {};\nconst bookingUid = (query.bookingUid || '').toString().trim();\nconst cleanerId = (query.cleanerId || '').toString().trim();\nconst response = (query.response || '').toString().trim().toLowerCase();\nreturn [{ json: { bookingUid, cleanerId, response } }];"
            },
            "id": "10b00003-aaaa-4bbb-cccc-dd0000000003",
            "name": "Parse Request",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
            "typeVersion": 2,
