                "message": "=You have accepted a cleaning job.\n\nProperty: {{ $('Build Accept Data').first().json.propertyName }}\nAddress: {{ $('Build Accept Data').first().json.address }}\n\nDate: {{ DateTime.fromISO($('Calculate Time').first().json.startTime, { zone: 'utc' }).toFormat('yyyy-MM-dd') }}\nTime: {{ DateTime.fromISO($('Calculate Time').first().json.startTime, { zone: 'utc' }).toFormat('HH:mm') }} - {{ DateTime.fromISO($('Calculate Time').first().json.endTime, { zone: 'utc' }).toFormat('HH:mm') }} UTC\n\nGuest Count: {{ parseInt($('Build Accept Data').first().json.adultCount || '0') + parseInt($('Build Accept Data').first().json.childrenCount || '0') }}\nBooking Reference: {{ $('Build Accept Data').first().json.bookingUid }}\n\nStep 1 \u2013 Clock In (on arrival):\n{{ $('Generate Links').first().json.clockInLink }}\n\nStep 2 \u2013 Checkout (when done):\n{{ $('Generate Links').first().json.checkoutLink }}\n\nThis email serves as official assignment confirmation.",
